cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY

The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning with actor-critic methods and agent modeling, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve cooperative and competitive multiagent scenarios, which also suggest the possibility of the paper belonging to the sub-categories of multiagent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the use of reinforcement learning in control systems can also relate to the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY).
